gloss: The mayor of Tijuana said Sunday he would not let the migrants' actions damage the city's relationship with the US and he is calling for the Mexican government to help with the situation.
text: The mayor of Tijuana said Sunday he would not let the migrants' actions damage the city's relationship with the US and he is calling for the Mexican government to help with the situation.
